snippet.title: Soul Hackers 2 — DLC Lineup | PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, PC
snippet.description:
Save humanity in style with the Soul Hackers 2 DLC! 

✨ 6 Outfit Packs
😈 8 Exclusive Demons
💥 DLC Story: The Lost Numbers
⬆️ Booster Item Pack


Pre-order the Soul Hackers 2 Digital Premium Edition and get access to all this DLC (and more) at launch! 

Learn more: soulhackers2.atlus.com
